what kind of placements do you deliver on the NewsBreak App

NewsBreak offers several types of ad placements to optimize performance. These include In-feed Ads, which integrate naturally within the app; In-Article placements, seamlessly embedded within premium publisher articles; Related Ads, which maximize engagement alongside relevant headlines; End of Article ads, offering personalized content based on reading preferences; and Immersive Flow, delivering full-screen video ads for maximum impact. You can find more details in our guide here: [Types of NewsBreak Ad Formats and Placements](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20229876903053-Types-of-NewsBreak-Ad-Formats-and-Placements).
if i can run weight loss products on NewsBreak

Advertising weight loss products on NewsBreak is subject to specific guidelines and policies. I recommend reviewing our Ad Policy document for detailed information on what is allowed. You can find it here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25362604231053-Ad-Policy). If you have any questions, feel free to ask!
